t will be curated through a rigorous process involving multiple models and human validation. Expected outcomes include a reliable benchmark suite that can be used to evaluate and compare multimodal models effectively, leading to improved model performance and transparency in AI research."\n}\n```', role='assistant', tool_calls=None, function_call=None, provider_specific_fields=None)
